1
00:00:21,700 --> 00:00:26,220
(Game Notice)
Welcome to the immersive simulation.

2
00:00:26,980 --> 00:00:33,140
Welcome to the open-world social
deduction game, Door of Truth.

3
00:00:33,140 --> 00:00:36,020
You'll enter the game world as a player

4
00:00:36,020 --> 00:00:38,740
and begin your character's adventure.

5
00:00:38,960 --> 00:00:41,480
This game contains four dungeons.

6
00:00:42,120 --> 00:00:43,720
(Four dungeons)
In each dungeon,

7
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:45,800
(Character)
you'll unlock a brand-new character,

8
00:00:45,800 --> 00:00:47,920
experience a different life,

9
00:00:47,920 --> 00:00:49,680
and meet the NPCs.

10
00:00:49,680 --> 00:00:51,760
Through exploration and interaction,

11
00:00:51,760 --> 00:00:54,880
you'll gradually uncover
each dungeon's unique story.

12
00:00:54,880 --> 00:00:56,000
Solve the case

13
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:57,480
and find the culprit.

14
00:00:57,480 --> 00:00:59,200
(Four dungeons complete)
Complete all four dungeons

15
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:01,160
to achieve the clear condition

16
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:02,800
(Clear achievement)
and unlock the hidden ending.

17
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,480
Each dungeon

18
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:05,600
(Case 1 Case 2)
may contain one

19
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:07,160
or more cases.

20
00:01:07,160 --> 00:01:08,400
(Random Detective Suspect)
Once a case begins,

21
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:10,400
players will be randomly
assigned as detectives

22
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:11,360
or suspects.

23
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:14,160
(Suspect NPC)
The culprit may be hiding

24
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:15,520
among the suspect players or the NPCs.

25
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:17,400
(Culprit)
Choose carefully.

26
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:19,240
The culprit's goal is to stay hidden

27
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:20,720
and avoid being caught.

28
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:23,400
(Culprit)
Only the culprit is allowed to lie.

29
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,760
(Main Quest, Evidence, Explore, Rewards)
During the case,

30
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:27,200
(Skill card, Trial, Stamina, Side quest)
players can trigger various mechanics

31
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:28,800
to advance the investigation.

32
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,800
Use them wisely,

33
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:32,400
and you might get a breakthrough.

34
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:34,800
(Suspect Culprit NPC)
When the case ends,

35
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:36,520
it's time to vote for the culprit.

36
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,680
If the culprit is identified,

37
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,120
(Correct vote Culprit)
players who voted correctly

38
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:42,200
will each receive a golden key.

39
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,840
If a player is the culprit

40
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:45,680
(Culprit Player)
and has the lowest vote count,

41
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:48,200
(Culprit Votes Player)
that culprit also receives a golden key.

42
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,960
(Player)
Golden keys will be tallied

43
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:52,560
at the end of each world.

44
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:54,920
(Skill card)
They can be redeemed for skill cards.

