Starlight Cafe.

116
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,920
(Starlight Cafe)

117
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:27,080
My absolute favorite!

118
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,720
First up,

119
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:33,480
