130
00:05:51,980 --> 00:05:53,900
(Barista: Ning Bubble)

131
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:54,520
Jin.

132
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:57,930
(Lemon sparkling Americano)
Today's special

133
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:58,840
for you is

134
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:02,120
the lemon sparkling Americano.

135
00:06:04,440 --> 00:06:05,760
I've already fainted.

136
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:07,280
If you want to wake me up,

137
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:10,840
you'll have to say my
name ten thousand times

138
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:12,260
