139
00:06:12,340 --> 00:06:14,020
(Life is tough,
gotta sing for my supper)

140
00:06:14,100 --> 00:06:19,100
(Seriously watching
a coworker do his thing)

141
00:06:20,820 --> 00:06:21,440
