149
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,780
Please, have a seat.

150
00:06:42,780 --> 00:06:44,060
(Feels sacred)

151
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:44,960
Go on.

152
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,920
Let out a nice fresh burp.

153
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,240
For the next one, I'd like

154
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:55,460
an Espresso Martini.

155
00:06:55,460 --> 00:06:56,460
(He Yiwei)

156
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,560
Barista He Yiwei.

157
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,600
Just standing there,

158
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,120
