159
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,520
Espresso Martini.

160
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:14,560
The only barista who
gets customers tipsy

161
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:17,120
before they even take a sip.

162
00:07:24,020 --> 00:07:28,620
(Barista: He Yiwei)

163
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:33,520
Your Espresso Martini.

164
00:07:34,300 --> 00:07:36,340
(Jin Cardashian, played by Jin Jing)

165
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,080
I choked.

166
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:38,640
Set it on the table.

167
00:07:38,640 --> 00:07:40,060
Smell it first.

168
00:07:40,060 --> 00:07:40,780
(Please follow my pace)

169
00:07:40,780 --> 00:07:42,420
(Too gracious to refuse)

170
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:43,320
What...

171
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:44,780
What does this mean?

172
00:07:44,860 --> 00:07:45,740
(He's got it all)

173
00:07:45,740 --> 00:07:47,700
(He Yiwei, played by Zhang Linghe)

174
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:48,520
May I sit down?

175
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:50,480
No.

176
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:51,500
(Who is he to sit with me?)
Yes.

177
00:07:52,900 --> 00:07:53,820
(Gone)

178
00:07:54,060 --> 00:07:55,340
(I'm "cof-free")

179
00:07:55,460 --> 00:07:57,260
(My bubbles)

180
00:07:59,220 --> 00:08:00,860
(Can someone do something)
Oh, my god.

181
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:07,680
(Helpful but clueless)
Where's the mop?

182
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,840
What is going on?

183
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,760
There's no need to
fight over a customer.

184
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,500
She wants mine!

185
00:08:12,620 --> 00:08:14,700
(Former coworkers come
to blows over a customer)

186
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:17,200
Stop it!

187
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:18,480
(I'd feel bad if any of you got hurt)
Jin is my customer!

188
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:19,120
Stop fighting!

189
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:19,840
Come on.

190
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:20,780
(Enthusiastic coworker)
Go fight for me!

191
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:22,280
(How dare you steal my customer)
He's stealing me.

192
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:23,720
Drag me away and steal me too!

193
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:24,760
(Directing)

194
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:25,480
Keep fighting.

195
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:26,740
(Playing along)
Okay.

196
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:27,760
Alright.

197
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:28,360
Come here!

198
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:28,880
No!

199
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:29,240
Enough.

200
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:29,760
I love you all!

201
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:31,400
(Ma'am, please calm down)
Jin, please sit.

202
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:34,030
Looks like she's not
impressed with Ning's drink.

203
00:08:34,140 --> 00:08:35,620
(The workplace is no joke)

204
00:08:35,760 --> 00:08:36,960
Next up,

205
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:39,120
