206
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,840
(Ding Pudding)
A pudding coffee,

207
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:41,960
Ding Pudding.

208
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,280
Barista Ding Pudding.

209
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:48,720
His coffee tastes just like him.

210
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,320
Sweet

211
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,120
