214
00:08:58,680 --> 00:08:59,560
And before you know it,

215
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:00,760
he's already stuck to your heart.

216
00:09:03,100 --> 00:09:05,620
(Barista: Ding Pudding)

217
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:06,320
Jin,

218
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:06,780
(Pudding coffee)

219
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,440
you're the extra sugar I added.

220
00:09:10,380 --> 00:09:12,100
(Sweet-talking his way into her heart)

221
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,040
Pudding.

222
00:09:19,540 --> 00:09:20,980
(A bit too sweet)

223
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,460
This is a little much for me.

224
00:09:22,460 --> 00:09:23,060
(Desperately need insulin)

225
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,320
When he turns it on like that,

226
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:26,080
