227
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:28,520
Alright,

228
00:09:28,520 --> 00:09:29,320
go ahead.

229
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:30,320
Top up my card.

230
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:31,920
On it.

231
00:09:31,920 --> 00:09:32,860
Top up.

232
00:09:32,860 --> 00:09:33,900
(Top seller of the month, confirmed)

233
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:34,520
Top up.

234
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:35,240
Next one.

235
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:39,160
That got me all flushed and worked up.

236
00:09:39,160 --> 00:09:40,960
I need something to cool me down.

237
00:09:40,980 --> 00:09:43,080
(Ke Coffee)
Triple mint cold brew.

238
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,400
Barista Ke Coffee.

239
00:09:48,160 --> 00:09:49,320
Love his face

240
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,640
