more than three words.

243
00:09:58,560 --> 00:10:00,200
The barista whose menu has no

244
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:01,380
"less ice" or "no ice."

245
00:10:01,500 --> 00:10:04,020
(Barista: Ke Coffee)

246
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:04,800
Triple mint cold brew.

247
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:06,100
Drink.

248
00:10:06,260 --> 00:10:09,500
(Triple mint cold brew,
ice cold to the end)

249
00:10:09,540 --> 00:10:10,940
(Gotta keep up the cool-guy image)

250
00:10:10,940 --> 00:10:12,660
