260
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:33,240
Crazy.

261
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:34,960
I've had so many drinks.

262
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:37,960
I'm honestly waterlogged.

263
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:39,120
So then,

264
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,680
