Didn't you just say you didn't go in?

3053
01:26:16,480 --> 01:26:17,760
Yeah, I said that.

3054
01:26:17,880 --> 01:26:20,600
Hopefully
she's the only one backtracking.

3055
01:26:20,600 --> 01:26:21,160
Hold on.

3056
01:26:21,160 --> 01:26:21,940
(I have something to say)

3057
01:26:23,440 --> 01:26:24,440
The last person

3058
01:26:24,440 --> 01:26:25,440
to admit it

3059
01:26:25,720 --> 01:26:26,720
is the most suspicious.

3060
01:26:28,520 --> 01:26:29,080
Sorry, everyone.

3061
01:26:29,480 --> 01:26:30,160
Actually...

3062
01:26:30,160 --> 01:26:31,840
I'm actually not done yet.

3063
01:26:31,840 --> 01:26:32,120
Let me...

3064
01:26:32,440 --> 01:26:33,280
No, let me go first.

3065
01:26:33,280 --> 01:26:33,880
I really...

3066
01:26:33,880 --> 01:26:34,560
I really need to go first.

3067
01:26:34,560 --> 01:26:34,920
Trust me.

3068
01:26:34,960 --> 01:26:35,400
What?

3069
01:26:35,400 --> 01:26:35,960
Trust you?

3070
01:26:36,320 --> 01:26:37,320
What's there to trust?

3071
01:26:37,320 --> 01:26:38,600
Why should we?

3072
01:26:38,600 --> 01:26:39,360
Because...

3073
01:26:39,640 --> 01:26:40,520
I think...

3074
01:26:41,240 --> 01:26:41,840
Yes.

3075
01:26:41,840 --> 01:26:42,880
I hit...

3076
01:26:42,880 --> 01:26:44,120
I fought him.

3077
01:26:44,720 --> 01:26:45,440
No.

3078
01:26:45,440 --> 01:26:47,000
I think it was me and him.

3079
01:26:48,040 --> 01:26:48,440
I think

3080
01:26:48,440 --> 01:26:49,640
it was me and him.

3081
01:26:52,520 --> 01:26:53,520
Of course I didn't.

3082
01:26:53,520 --> 01:26:54,320
No way.

3083
01:26:54,680 --> 01:26:55,160
I did go

3084
01:26:55,160 --> 01:26:56,880
into the VIP room.

3085
01:26:56,880 --> 01:26:57,880
I absolutely never went in.

3086
01:26:57,880 --> 01:26:58,360
I never went in.

3087
01:26:58,360 --> 01:26:59,000
I went over

3088
01:26:59,000 --> 01:27:00,680
and bam, I hit him.

3089
01:27:00,680 --> 01:27:02,000
Why all the questions?

3090
01:27:02,000 --> 01:27:03,560
Then we fought, and I grabbed his hair.

3091
01:27:03,720 --> 01:27:04,960
We were working.

3092
01:27:05,040 --> 01:27:06,040
All of a sudden,

3093
01:27:06,040 --> 01:27:06,960
I just...

3094
01:27:06,960 --> 01:27:07,520
passed out.

3095
01:27:07,880 --> 01:27:08,680
My head hurts so bad.

3096
01:27:08,940 --> 01:27:11,620
(Why did all four lie
about going in the VIP room?)

3097
01:27:11,700 --> 01:27:12,440
(Preview)

3098
01:27:12,440 --> 01:27:13,600
(Searching trash for signs of life)
This much garbage?

3099
01:27:13,600 --> 01:27:14,680
Are you kidding me?

3100
01:27:15,440 --> 01:27:16,280
There's a snake!

3101
01:27:16,280 --> 01:27:17,120
What?

3102
01:27:18,440 --> 01:27:19,240
Tui Haomei?

3103
01:27:19,240 --> 01:27:20,200
(Tui Haomei)
Tell us where you are.

3104
01:27:20,220 --> 01:27:20,960
(Desire leads into darkness)

3105
01:27:20,960 --> 01:27:22,040
Why are the lights on now?

3106
01:27:22,280 --> 01:27:23,360
That's the light inside there.

3107
01:27:23,360 --> 01:27:25,240
So there are two identical spaces.

3108
01:27:25,240 --> 01:27:25,880
What?

3109
01:27:25,880 --> 01:27:27,040
There's another place inside.

3110
01:27:27,040 --> 01:27:27,760
Search it.

3111
01:27:27,760 --> 01:27:28,320
A secret passage.

3112
01:27:28,960 --> 01:27:30,480
This must be the boss's

3113
01:27:30,480 --> 01:27:31,520
