3114
01:27:31,880 --> 01:27:33,040
What is this?

3115
01:27:33,040 --> 01:27:34,240
I've never done this.

3116
01:27:34,240 --> 01:27:36,040
I never filmed that video earlier.

3117
01:27:36,040 --> 01:27:37,800
His business model is written below.

3118
01:27:37,800 --> 01:27:38,520
Small profits, high volume.

3119
01:27:38,520 --> 01:27:39,520
All profit.

3120
01:27:39,520 --> 01:27:40,720
Vicious cycle.

3121
01:27:40,720 --> 01:27:41,760
Endless cash machine.

3122
01:27:41,920 --> 01:27:42,200
Wait.

3123
01:27:42,200 --> 01:27:43,160
Why is there blood here?

3124
01:27:43,320 --> 01:27:43,960
What's this?

3125
01:27:43,960 --> 01:27:44,360
Hold on.

3126
01:27:44,360 --> 01:27:44,880
What's this?

3127
01:27:44,880 --> 01:27:45,800
It's a girl.

3128
01:27:45,800 --> 01:27:47,320
Is this Tui Haomei?

3129
01:27:47,320 --> 01:27:48,520
She wrote in blood.

3130
01:27:48,520 --> 01:27:49,920
What exactly is our boss doing?

3131
01:27:49,920 --> 01:27:51,160
He killed my girlfriend.

3132
01:27:51,160 --> 01:27:52,360
So I'm going to kill the boss.

3133
01:27:52,360 --> 01:27:54,360
I can prove I'm clear on this point.

3134
01:27:54,360 --> 01:27:55,720
Prove yourself?

3135
01:27:55,720 --> 01:27:57,480
That sentence makes no sense.

3136
01:27:57,480 --> 01:27:58,880
Everyone had motive,

3137
01:27:58,880 --> 01:27:59,800
and everyone acted on it.

3138
01:27:59,800 --> 01:28:01,120
That doesn't apply to me.

3139
01:28:01,120 --> 01:28:03,000
By that logic,
none of us were under threat.

3140
01:28:03,000 --> 01:28:04,080
Which part don't you believe?

3141
01:28:04,320 --> 01:28:05,080
But from where I'm standing,

3142
01:28:05,080 --> 01:28:06,020
I'm more suspicious of you.

3143
01:28:06,140 --> 01:28:07,700
(Under the stars, secrets linger)

3144
01:28:55,680 --> 01:28:59,680
♪Come now, players all,
let the game of reason start♪

3145
01:28:59,680 --> 01:29:04,120
